.TH SENTINEL-MODELS 1 "2026-03-08" "SENTINEL 0.1.0" "SENTINEL Manual"
.SH NAME
sentinel-models \- list available Ollama models and preview model matrices
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B python3 list_models.py
.RI [ OPTIONS ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Lists all models available in the local Ollama instance with their sizes
and digests. Optionally generates a model matrix preview showing how
models would be assigned to agents for matrix experiments.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI \-\-matrix " CONFIG"
Path to experiment config JSON. When provided, generates a model matrix
preview showing agent-to-model assignments.
.TP
.BI \-\-mode " MODE"
Matrix mode for preview: homogeneous, asymmetric, or mixed.
Default: homogeneous.
.TP
.BI \-\-models " LIST"
Comma-separated model names to include. Default: all available.
.SH EXAMPLES
List all available models:
.PP
.RS
python3 list_models.py
.RE
.PP
Preview asymmetric matrix:
.PP
.RS
python3 list_models.py \-\-matrix config/three_agent_mesh.json \\
    \-\-mode asymmetric
.RE
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR sentinel-matrix (1)
